{
  "texts": [
    "We divide each model into several execution steps and allocate different numbers of functional cores to them as presented in Fig. 6e.",
    "The flexible timing schedule of TianjicX enables a pipelined execution of the steps for better performance.",
    "As summarized in Fig. 6f, both DH-SNNs can be efficiently performed on TianjicX with high throughput and low power consumption.",
    "More details of hardware implementation are provided in Methods and Supplementary Fig.",
    "In the field of brain-computer interface, how to handle electroencephalogram (EEG) signals effectively is a significant problem."
  ]
}